STATE
v.
DORNOFF 2018-1125 Supreme Court of Ohio. October 24, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

On review of an order certifying a conflict. The court determines that a conflict exists. Sua sponte, cause held for the decision in 2017-1703, State v. Dangler, and briefing schedule stayed.
